n="00:19.647" end="00:23.628" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:19.647" end="00:20.572">Makin'</span> <span begin="00:20.572" end="00:21.405">sweet</span> <span begin="00:21.405" end="00:22.122">love,</span> <span begin="00:22.122" end="00:22.801">takin'</span> <span begin="00:22.801" end="00:23.628">time</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">温柔缠绵 慢慢享受时光</span></p><p begin="00:25.789" end="00:27.165" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:25.789" end="00:26.043">Till</span> <span begin="00:26.043" end="00:26.377">God</span> <span begin="00:26.377" end="00:26.693">strikes</span> <span begin="00:26.693" end="00:27.165">us</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">直到神明降下惩罚</span></p><p begin="00:29.689" end="00:32.235" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:29.689" end="00:29.890">That's</span> <span begin="00:29.890" end="00:30.157">a</span> <span begin="00:30.157" end="00:30.557">pretty</span> <span begin="00:30.557" end="00:30.972">fuckin'</span> <span begin="00:30.972" end="00:31.289">fast</span> <span begin="00:31.289" end="00:31.573">year</span> <span begin="00:31.573" end="00:31.805">flew</span> <span begin="00:31.805" end="00:32.235">by</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">这一年过得真快</span></p><p begin="00:37.074" end="00:39.619" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:37.074" end="00:37.284">That's</span> <span begin="00:37.284" end="00:37.516">a</span> <span begin="00:37.516" end="00:37.931">pretty</span> <span begin="00:37.931" end="00:38.261">long</span> <span begin="00:38.261" end="00:38.578">third</span> <span begin="00:38.578" end="00:38.802">gear</span> <span begin="00:38.802" end="00:38.951">in</span> <span begin="00:38.951" end="00:39.186">this</span> <span begin="00:39.186" end="00:39.619">car</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">车挂在三档 开了很久</span></p><p begin="00:40.312" end="00:41.523" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:40.312" end="00:40.713">Glidin'</span> <span begin="00:40.713" end="00:40.931">on</span> <span begin="00:40.931" end="00:41.114">the</span> <span begin="00:41.114" end="00:41.523">5</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在 5 号公路上滑行</span></p><p begin="00:42.046" end="00:45.280" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:42.046" end="00:42.189">The</span> <span begin="00:42.189" end="00:42.541">deer</span> <span begin="00:42.541" end="00:42.755">run</span> <span begin="00:42.755" end="00:43.449">across,</span> <span begin="00:44.040" end="00:44.324">kill</span> <span begin="00:44.324" end="00:44.507">the</span> <span begin="00:44.507" end="00:45.280">headlights</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">有鹿跑过 熄灭车头灯</span></p><p begin="00:46.713" end="00:47.709" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:46.713" end="00:47.148">Pretty</span> <span begin="00:47.148" end="00:47.709">fuckin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真是美妙</span></p><p begin="00:48.535" end="00:50.424" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:48.535" end="00:49.257">Underneath</span> <span begin="00:49.257" end="00:49.910">moonlight</span> <span begin="00:49.910" end="00:50.424">now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">沐浴在月光下</span></p><p begin="00:54.088" end="00:55.174" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:54.088" end="00:54.595">Pretty</span> <span begin="00:54.595" end="00:55.174">fuckin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">真是美妙</span></p><p begin="00:55.849" end="00:57.605" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:55.849" end="00:56.586">Sunrise</span> <span begin="00:56.586" end="00:56.952">in</span> <span begin="00:56.952" end="00:57.605">sight</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">日出在望</span></p><p begin="00:57.041" end="01:01.380" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:57.041" end="00:58.263">In</span> <span begin="00:58.263" end="00:58.611">comes</span> <span begin="00:58.611" end="00:58.878">the</span> <span begin="00:58.878" end="00:59.296">mornin',</span> <span begin="00:59.296" end="00:59.778">hauntin'</span> <span begin="00:59.778" end="01:00.012">us</span> <span begin="01:00.012" end="01:00.197">with</span> <span begin="01:00.197" end="01:00.465">the</span> <span begin="01:00.465" end="01:01.380">beams</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">清晨来临 阳光如影随形</span></p><p begin="01:01.495" end="01:05.145" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="01:01.495" end="01:02.101">Solstice</span> <span begin="01:02.101" end="01:02.317">ain't</span> <span begin="01:02.317" end="01:02.535">as</span> <span begin="01:02.535" end="01:02.783">far</span> <span begin="01:02.783" end="01:03.018">as</span> <span begin="01:03.018" end="01:03.250">it</span> <span begin="01:03.250" end="01:03.917">used</span> <span begin="01:03.917" end="01:04.167">to</span> <span begin="01:04.167" end="01:05.145">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夏至不再像从前那般遥远</span></p><p begin="01:05.264" end="01:07.942" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:05.264" end="01:05.546">It</span> <span begin="01:05.546" end="01:05.996">begins</span> <span begin="01:05.996" end="01:06.263">to</span> <span begin="01:06.263" end="01:06.498">blur,</span> <span begin="01:06.498" end="01:06.748">we</span> <span begin="01:06.748" end="01:06.980">get</span> <span begin="01:06.980" end="01:07.435">ol</span><span begin="01:07.435" end="01:07.942">der</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:08.889" end="01:09.591"><span begin="01:08.889" end="01:09.591">(Blur)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">模糊</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">一切开始模糊 我们渐渐老去</span></p><p begin="01:12.447" end="01:16.016" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:12.447" end="01:13.141">Summer's</span> <span begin="01:13.141" end="01:13.391">not</span> <span begin="01:13.391" end="01:13.626">as</span> <span begin="01:13.626" end="01:13.876">long</span> <span begin="01:13.876" end="01:14.108">as</span> <span begin="01:14.108" end="01:14.358">it</span> <span begin="01:14.358" end="01:14.941">used</span> <span begin="01:14.941" end="01:15.400">to</span> <span begin="01:15.400" end="01:16.016">be</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夏天不再像从前那般漫长</span></p><p begin="01:16.316" end="01:18.971" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:16.316" end="01:16.928">Every</span> <span begin="01:16.928" end="01:17.244">day</span> <span begin="01:17.244" end="01:17.662">counts</span> <span begin="01:17.662" end="01:17.993">like</span> <span begin="01:17.993" end="01:18.971">crazy</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:19.371" end="01:22.010"><span begin="01:19.371" end="01:20.156">(Smoke,</span> <span begin="01:21.316" end="01:22.010">haze)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">烟雾 迷蒙</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">每一天都无比珍贵</span></p><p begin="01:23.411" end="01:24.678" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:23.411" end="01:23.755">Wanna</span> <span begin="01:23.755" end="01:23.936">get</span> <span begin="01:23.936" end="01:24.678">soaked?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想不想全身湿透</span></p><p begin="01:25.037" end="01:26.634" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:25.037" end="01:25.347">Wanna</span> <span begin="01:25.347" end="01:25.480">film</span> <span begin="01:25.480" end="01:25.597">a</span> <span begin="01:25.597" end="01:25.813">tape</span> <span begin="01:25.813" end="01:25.971">on</span> <span begin="01:25.971" end="01:26.168">the</span> <span begin="01:26.168" end="01:26.248">speed</span> <span begin="01:26.248" end="01:26.634">boat?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">想不想在快艇上拍段录像</span></p><p begin="01:27.064" end="01:29.914" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:27.064" end="01:27.425">We</span> <span begin="01:27.425" end="01:27.840">smell</span> <span begin="01:27.840" end="01:28.107">of</span> <span begin="01:28.107" end="01:29.454">Californica</span><span begin="01:29.454" end="01:29.914">tion</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="01:28.910" end="01:29.634"><span begin="01:28.910" end="01:29.118">(Strike</span> <span begin="01:29.118" end="01:29.252">a</span> <span begin="01:29.252" end="01:29.634">pose)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">摆个姿势</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">我们散发着《加州靡情》的气息</span></p><p begin="01:30.534" end="01:33.376" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:30.534" end="01:31.061">Everything</span> <span begin="01:31.061" end="01:31.325">grows</span> <span begin="01:31.325" end="01:31.458">in</span> <span begin="01:31.458" end="01:31.592">the</span> <span begin="01:31.592" end="01:32.100">Congo,</span> <span begin="01:32.436" end="01:32.868">everything</span> <span begin="01:32.868" end="01:33.376">grows</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">在刚果 万物生长 万物生长</span></p><p begin="01:32.191" end="01:39.772" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:32.191" end="01:32.987">Ooh,</span> <span begin="01:32.987" end="01:34.002">ooh,</span> <span begin="01:34.002" end="01:34.385">can</span> <span begin="01:34.385" end="01:34.719">you</span> <span begin="01:34.719" end="01:36.042">come</span> <span begin="01:36.431" end="01:36.814">when</span> <span begin="01:36.814" end="01:37.162">I</span> <span begin="01:37.162" end="01:37.679">call</span> <span begin="01:37.679" end="01:39.772">again?</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">噢 噢 当我再次呼唤 你会来吗</span></p><p begin="02:10.809" end="02:14.212" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="02:10.809" end="02:12.155">On</span> <span begin="02:12.155" end="02:12.485">comes</span> <span begin="02:12.485" end="02:12.721">the</span> <span begin="02:12.721" end="02:13.084">eve</span><span begin="02:13.084" end="02:14.212">nin'</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">夜幕降临</span></p><p begin="02:14.484" end="02:17.817" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="02:14.484" end="02:15.719">Gold</span> <span begin="02:15.719" end="02:16.337">seekin'</span> <span begin="02:16.337" end="02:17.817">ends</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">不再追名逐利</span></p><p begin="02:18.161" end="02:23.301" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="02:18.161" end="02:19.580">Piece</span> <span begin="02:19.580" end="02:19.847">in</span> <span begin="02:19.847" end="02:20.164">my</span> <span begin="02:20.164" end="02:20.596">hand</span> <span begin="02:20.596" end="02:21.064">worth</span> <span begin="02:21.064" end="02:21.331">twice</span> <span begin="02:21.331" end="02:21.496">than</span> <span begin="02:21.496" end="02:21.696">a</span> <span begin="02:21.696" end="02:23.301">friend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">手中的东西 胜过双倍的友谊</span></p><p begin="02:24.575" end="02:32.841" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="02:24.575" end="02:24.915">And</span> <span begin="02:24.915" end="02:25.551">two</span> <span begin="02:25.551" end="02:26.901">limbs</span> <span begin="02:26.901" end="02:27.351">over</span> <span begin="02:27.351" end="02:27.822">shoul</span><span begin="02:27.822" end="02:29.020">der,</span> <span begin="02:29.290" end="02:30.541">car</span><span begin="02:30.541" end="02:31.016">ried</span> <span begin="02:31.016" end="02:31.272">a</span><span begin="02:31.272" end="02:32.841">way</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">双臂搭上肩头 忘乎所以</span></p><p begin="02:34.067" end="02:39.442" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:34.067" end="02:34.562">Because</span> <span begin="02:34.562" end="02:34.779">I'm</span> <span begin="02:34.779" end="02:35.128">stron</span><span begin="02:35.128" end="02:36.211">ger,</span> <span begin="02:36.395" end="02:36.643">the</span> <span begin="02:36.643" end="02:37.991">Congo</span> <span begin="02:37.991" end="02:38.332">is</span> <span begin="02:38.332" end="02:39.442">dim</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:35.573" end="02:39.445"><span begin="02:35.573" end="02:36.813">(Stronger,</span> <span begin="02:38.969" end="02:39.445">smoke)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">更强大 烟雾</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">因为我更强大 刚果也黯然失色</span></p><p begin="02:40.365" end="02:46.179" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:40.365" end="02:41.688">In</span> <span begin="02:41.688" end="02:42.071">comes</span> <span begin="02:42.071" end="02:42.356">the</span> <span begin="02:42.356" end="02:42.704">mor</span><span begin="02:42.704" end="02:43.621">nin',</span> <span begin="02:43.621" end="02:46.179">ah</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:46.179" end="02:46.844"><span begin="02:46.179" end="02:46.844">(Smoke)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">烟雾</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">清晨来临 啊</span></p><p begin="02:47.742" end="02:55.394" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:47.742" end="02:49.025">In</span> <span begin="02:49.025" end="02:49.359">comes</span> <span begin="02:49.359" end="02:49.693">the</span> <span begin="02:49.693" end="02:49.963">mor</span><span begin="02:49.963" end="02:51.042">nin',</span> <span begin="02:51.042" end="02:55.394">ah</span> <span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="02:53.687" end="02:54.260"><span begin="02:53.687" end="02:54.260">(Haze)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">迷蒙</span></span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-CN">清晨来临 啊</span></p></div></body></tt>